00:00:26.982 --> 00:00:28.690 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA MEREDITH:
Have you ever wondered

00:00:28.690 --> 00:00:30.940 align:middle line:10%
why so many people in
the New Age movement

00:00:30.940 --> 00:00:33.395 align:middle line:10%
have had a rough time
dealing with life, finances,

00:00:33.395 --> 00:00:34.760 align:middle line:10%
and the like?

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:38.210 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps it's because we've been
misinformed and even distracted

00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:41.170 align:middle line:84%
by promises of prosperity,
without encouraging

00:00:41.170 --> 00:00:43.630 align:middle line:84%
our deep development
as the underpinnings

00:00:43.630 --> 00:00:45.140 align:middle line:90%
to a life well-lived.

00:00:45.140 --> 00:00:48.140 align:middle line:84%
To understand the lineage of
so much conflicting information

00:00:48.140 --> 00:00:50.250 align:middle line:84%
in the self-actualization
movement,

00:00:50.250 --> 00:00:52.930 align:middle line:84%
it's a delight for me to have
our guest today, Nigel Taylor,

00:00:52.930 --> 00:00:54.420 align:middle line:90%
with us once again.

00:00:54.420 --> 00:00:57.572 align:middle line:84%
We had a fabulous
conversation a couple of weeks

00:00:57.572 --> 00:00:58.530 align:middle line:90%
ago leading up to this.

00:00:58.530 --> 00:01:00.571 align:middle line:84%
I was going to go a
different direction with you,

00:01:00.571 --> 00:01:03.370 align:middle line:84%
but it was so interesting,
this is where we are.

00:01:03.370 --> 00:01:04.822 align:middle line:84%
And we had so much
fun last time.

00:01:04.822 --> 00:01:07.280 align:middle line:84%
>>NIGEL TAYLOR: Yes we did,
and it's a pleasure to be back.

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:08.550 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So let's start.

00:01:08.550 --> 00:01:11.200 align:middle line:84%
You said, just a moment ago,
before the camera came on,

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:13.750 align:middle line:84%
that you were giving
more thought to where

00:01:13.750 --> 00:01:16.160 align:middle line:84%
this whole lineage that
became known as the "New Age"

00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:18.290 align:middle line:90%
movement began.

00:01:18.290 --> 00:01:22.770 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Well, if you look at
what the New Age per se means,

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:25.650 align:middle line:84%
it is the dawning of
this new consciousness.

00:01:25.650 --> 00:01:27.300 align:middle line:84%
And the dawning of
a new consciousness,

00:01:27.300 --> 00:01:30.740 align:middle line:84%
if we actually track back,
has got different plateaus

00:01:30.740 --> 00:01:33.920 align:middle line:84%
upon which it has
reached its position.

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:38.090 align:middle line:10%
One of the primary elements
which brought it forward

00:01:38.090 --> 00:01:40.630 align:middle line:10%
was the time of
the Rosicrucians.

00:01:40.630 --> 00:01:44.850 align:middle line:10%
And that's going back to 1612,
1616, when the Rosicrucian

00:01:44.850 --> 00:01:46.160 align:middle line:10%
manifesto came out.

00:01:46.160 --> 00:01:48.240 align:middle line:10%
And it was very secretive.

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:50.720 align:middle line:84%
And the whole principle
behind that manifesto

00:01:50.720 --> 00:01:53.750 align:middle line:84%
was that at times of
great persecution,

00:01:53.750 --> 00:01:57.350 align:middle line:84%
there would be a way to
communicate hidden truths.

00:01:57.350 --> 00:01:59.600 align:middle line:84%
And those truths
permeated their way

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:03.230 align:middle line:84%
through in the Age of Reason
and the Age of Enlightenment,

00:02:03.230 --> 00:02:07.470 align:middle line:84%
because it was shortly after
that that we had Descartes.

00:02:07.470 --> 00:02:12.030 align:middle line:84%
And then from Descartes
came a significant issue

00:02:12.030 --> 00:02:15.670 align:middle line:84%
of dualism, which he
never really intended

00:02:15.670 --> 00:02:16.970 align:middle line:90%
to come out of his teachings.

00:02:16.970 --> 00:02:18.890 align:middle line:84%
Because in his
second meditation,

00:02:18.890 --> 00:02:23.480 align:middle line:84%
he alluded to the fact that in
actual fact, there is only one,

00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:25.484 align:middle line:84%
and this is an illusion
in which we are dancing.

00:02:25.484 --> 00:02:27.400 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: See, that's
not the part we're told.

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:29.690 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Yeah, well, this
is-- but see, what happens,

00:02:29.690 --> 00:02:30.856 align:middle line:90%
and it's the same old story.

00:02:30.856 --> 00:02:33.470 align:middle line:84%
Where did the Age
of Reason come from?

00:02:33.470 --> 00:02:40.580 align:middle line:84%
It came from the failings of the
institutions that preceded it,

00:02:40.580 --> 00:02:44.230 align:middle line:84%
which controlled the
mystical elements of life.

00:02:44.230 --> 00:02:45.730 align:middle line:84%
And so the
Rosicrucians said, OK.

00:02:45.730 --> 00:02:48.722 align:middle line:84%
Well, let's see if we can
bring this back and make it--

00:02:48.722 --> 00:02:49.555 align:middle line:90%
it's still mystical.

00:02:49.555 --> 00:02:52.790 align:middle line:84%
Let's see if we can
reintroduce it to those

00:02:52.790 --> 00:02:55.050 align:middle line:90%
who are willing to do the work.

00:02:55.050 --> 00:02:58.290 align:middle line:84%
And so doing the work
is the primary issue.

00:02:58.290 --> 00:03:00.870 align:middle line:84%
And out of that
movement there have

00:03:00.870 --> 00:03:04.640 align:middle line:84%
been many, many developments
from the 1600s, 1700s, 1800s.

00:03:04.640 --> 00:03:06.910 align:middle line:84%
You bring yourself
right up to the--

00:03:06.910 --> 00:03:08.660 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Let's say
to the 1920s and '30s.

00:03:08.660 --> 00:03:10.150 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Well,
the 1920s and '30s,

00:03:10.150 --> 00:03:11.691 align:middle line:84%
you've got the
Theosophical movement.

00:03:11.691 --> 00:03:12.550 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:03:12.550 --> 00:03:15.370 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: With the
Theosophical movement

00:03:15.370 --> 00:03:17.170 align:middle line:84%
and the Anthroposophical
movement--

00:03:17.170 --> 00:03:18.290 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, Steiner.

00:03:18.290 --> 00:03:20.800 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Those primary
movements and Steiner

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:26.680 align:middle line:84%
were people who were actually
rational thinkers, in that they

00:03:26.680 --> 00:03:29.540 align:middle line:90%
were scientifically based.

00:03:29.540 --> 00:03:32.300 align:middle line:84%
That they were
looking at a pathway

00:03:32.300 --> 00:03:35.090 align:middle line:90%
to refine consciousness.

00:03:35.090 --> 00:03:38.040 align:middle line:84%
And there's a very
important element here.

00:03:38.040 --> 00:03:42.190 align:middle line:84%
The key is the
refining of the mind.

00:03:42.190 --> 00:03:44.480 align:middle line:84%
Now, if you look at
where we are today,

00:03:44.480 --> 00:03:46.800 align:middle line:84%
and this is a
generalization, because it's

00:03:46.800 --> 00:03:51.570 align:middle line:84%
very unfair to take a brush
and sweep it across everybody.

00:03:51.570 --> 00:03:54.437 align:middle line:84%
But there's been a move
away from the refining

00:03:54.437 --> 00:03:55.145 align:middle line:90%
of consciousness.

00:03:55.145 --> 00:03:56.560 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Boy, has there been.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:58.870 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: And see, if you
go through like you said,

00:03:58.870 --> 00:04:01.780 align:middle line:84%
you have the mystery
schools, like BOTA.

00:04:01.780 --> 00:04:04.940 align:middle line:84%
Preceding that was
the Golden Dawn.

00:04:04.940 --> 00:04:07.440 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, and I think of
that the Rosicrucian doctrine

00:04:07.440 --> 00:04:10.150 align:middle line:84%
was loosely based on a lot of
the ancient, ancient hermetic

00:04:10.150 --> 00:04:10.330 align:middle line:90%
doctrine.

00:04:10.330 --> 00:04:11.620 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: It goes
back-- if you go back

00:04:11.620 --> 00:04:13.494 align:middle line:84%
to the hermetic doctrine,
you can keep going.

00:04:13.494 --> 00:04:14.660 align:middle line:90%
We can push this way back.

00:04:14.660 --> 00:04:14.704 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:04:14.704 --> 00:04:15.420 align:middle line:90%
Back to Atlantis.

00:04:15.420 --> 00:04:16.130 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: And even beyond.

00:04:16.130 --> 00:04:17.004 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: And beyond.

00:04:17.004 --> 00:04:19.620 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: So in this
current time frame

00:04:19.620 --> 00:04:21.560 align:middle line:84%
that we're looking
at, what we've got

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:25.120 align:middle line:84%
is the mystery schools,
which have grown out

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:27.320 align:middle line:90%
of the different traditions.

00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:30.130 align:middle line:84%
And then we come
to a place where

00:04:30.130 --> 00:04:33.630 align:middle line:84%
we had the development
of teachers

00:04:33.630 --> 00:04:35.220 align:middle line:84%
that were very,
very well respected

00:04:35.220 --> 00:04:37.850 align:middle line:90%
inside the American system.

00:04:37.850 --> 00:04:41.800 align:middle line:84%
Those were the likes of say,
US Anderson, Dale Carnegie.

00:04:41.800 --> 00:04:43.380 align:middle line:90%
This is how we think.

00:04:43.380 --> 00:04:46.690 align:middle line:84%
This is the power of
positive thinking.

00:04:46.690 --> 00:04:51.100 align:middle line:84%
Once the '60s came, there
was the Vietnam War.

00:04:51.100 --> 00:04:52.580 align:middle line:90%
There was the Age of Aquarius.

00:04:52.580 --> 00:04:53.730 align:middle line:90%
This is the time.

00:04:53.730 --> 00:04:55.240 align:middle line:84%
This is where the
change has come.

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:56.960 align:middle line:84%
Everybody wanted to
change everything.

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:58.570 align:middle line:84%
That was the field
of information

00:04:58.570 --> 00:04:59.490 align:middle line:90%
which was out there.

00:04:59.490 --> 00:05:00.698 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: The Leo generation.

00:05:00.698 --> 00:05:04.850 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: The Leo generation.
[CHUCKLES] Now, what happened--

00:05:04.850 --> 00:05:07.810 align:middle line:84%
and this is, again,
an observation--

00:05:07.810 --> 00:05:12.130 align:middle line:84%
was the move was away from
personal responsibility

00:05:12.130 --> 00:05:15.490 align:middle line:84%
in your journey
of life to let me

00:05:15.490 --> 00:05:20.920 align:middle line:84%
get an outcome with the easiest
possible path available.

00:05:20.920 --> 00:05:24.510 align:middle line:84%
So rather than
necessarily saying,

00:05:24.510 --> 00:05:26.130 align:middle line:90%
there's a law of attraction.

00:05:26.130 --> 00:05:26.630 align:middle line:90%
All right?

00:05:26.630 --> 00:05:28.980 align:middle line:84%
Now, the law of
attraction-- which

00:05:28.980 --> 00:05:31.990 align:middle line:84%
became very big with "The
Secret," et cetera-- the law

00:05:31.990 --> 00:05:33.170 align:middle line:90%
of attraction is, OK, fine.

00:05:33.170 --> 00:05:36.890 align:middle line:84%
If I put this thought out,
I would attract to me,

00:05:36.890 --> 00:05:39.220 align:middle line:84%
and I will walk
into this reality.

00:05:39.220 --> 00:05:40.560 align:middle line:90%
That's fine.

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:44.340 align:middle line:84%
But the very foundations of
what it was actually all about

00:05:44.340 --> 00:05:50.320 align:middle line:84%
was ripped away by the desire
and by the need, if you will,

00:05:50.320 --> 00:05:53.170 align:middle line:84%
by some elements in
the community that

00:05:53.170 --> 00:05:55.290 align:middle line:90%
wanted to teach this.

00:05:55.290 --> 00:05:56.890 align:middle line:84%
To show people
you could actually

00:05:56.890 --> 00:05:59.910 align:middle line:84%
create miracles
inside the dream.

00:05:59.910 --> 00:06:03.450 align:middle line:84%
But the real issue
is, if you create

00:06:03.450 --> 00:06:07.070 align:middle line:84%
an outcome inside this
dream which we live,

00:06:07.070 --> 00:06:08.990 align:middle line:90%
there are always consequences.

00:06:08.990 --> 00:06:12.240 align:middle line:84%
There are always going
to be ramifications

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:14.927 align:middle line:84%
for the way in which
you use consciousness.

00:06:14.927 --> 00:06:15.510 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:06:15.510 --> 00:06:17.960 align:middle line:84%
And most of those miracles
that we were promised actually

00:06:17.960 --> 00:06:20.560 align:middle line:84%
did not manifest in
most people's lives.

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:21.830 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: Absolutely.

00:06:21.830 --> 00:06:25.330 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I mean, the proof is
in the pudding, as they say.

00:06:25.330 --> 00:06:28.120 align:middle line:84%
And yet, people would
still buy the books,

00:06:28.120 --> 00:06:30.530 align:middle line:84%
go to the conferences,
spend millions of dollars,

00:06:30.530 --> 00:06:31.420 align:middle line:90%
collectively.

00:06:31.420 --> 00:06:36.480 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Well, let me share
a lesson that I encountered

00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:39.100 align:middle line:90%
very early in the piece.

00:06:39.100 --> 00:06:42.340 align:middle line:84%
Way back when I started
teaching these principles,

00:06:42.340 --> 00:06:44.080 align:middle line:84%
I had a gentleman
who went through.

00:06:44.080 --> 00:06:47.810 align:middle line:84%
And I had taught the very
foundations of consciousness,

00:06:47.810 --> 00:06:50.420 align:middle line:84%
as I understood it
at that time in which

00:06:50.420 --> 00:06:54.500 align:middle line:84%
I taught it, which I'm happy
to say has considerably

00:06:54.500 --> 00:06:57.400 align:middle line:84%
moved, and therefore,
has taught me a lesson.

00:06:57.400 --> 00:07:00.160 align:middle line:84%
But this gentleman
came in, and he

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:02.600 align:middle line:84%
went through the whole
training and everything we did.

00:07:02.600 --> 00:07:03.570 align:middle line:90%
It went for five days.

00:07:03.570 --> 00:07:05.700 align:middle line:90%
It was pretty intense.

00:07:05.700 --> 00:07:09.360 align:middle line:84%
And then, I'm guessing it was
probably about six months,

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:10.630 align:middle line:90%
a year later.

00:07:10.630 --> 00:07:13.990 align:middle line:84%
He turned up, and he
said, I've got this idea.

00:07:13.990 --> 00:07:15.602 align:middle line:90%
I thought, great.

00:07:15.602 --> 00:07:16.310 align:middle line:90%
Share it with me.

00:07:16.310 --> 00:07:17.430 align:middle line:90%
What is it?

00:07:17.430 --> 00:07:23.250 align:middle line:84%
And he shared this
goal, if you will,

00:07:23.250 --> 00:07:29.720 align:middle line:84%
that the largest piece of jade
which existed on the planet,

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:34.470 align:middle line:84%
he was going to actually
convince the owner of this, who

00:07:34.470 --> 00:07:37.590 align:middle line:84%
he didn't know and had
no direct connections to,

00:07:37.590 --> 00:07:40.040 align:middle line:84%
to actually sell
it, and he would

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:45.940 align:middle line:84%
make some huge sum of
commission on the sale of that.

00:07:45.940 --> 00:07:47.870 align:middle line:84%
And I asked him, I
said, well, how exactly

00:07:47.870 --> 00:07:48.911 align:middle line:90%
are you going to do that?

00:07:48.911 --> 00:07:50.490 align:middle line:84%
And he said, well,
I'm visualizing.

00:07:50.490 --> 00:07:52.060 align:middle line:90%
I'm meditating.

00:07:52.060 --> 00:07:55.000 align:middle line:90%
I'm believing and I'm affirming.

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:58.320 align:middle line:84%
You think it'll
happen, won't it?

00:07:58.320 --> 00:08:01.285 align:middle line:84%
And I said, I can't
say that that's

00:08:01.285 --> 00:08:02.660 align:middle line:90%
the thing I would be doing.

00:08:02.660 --> 00:08:04.650 align:middle line:84%
And he said, well,
I believe, and I'm

00:08:04.650 --> 00:08:05.670 align:middle line:90%
going to make it happen.

00:08:05.670 --> 00:08:08.370 align:middle line:90%
Belief, desire, expectancy.

00:08:08.370 --> 00:08:11.480 align:middle line:84%
Well, I saw him, I guess, I'm
going to say a year later.

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:14.250 align:middle line:84%
It might have been a
bit-- he lost everything.

00:08:14.250 --> 00:08:16.140 align:middle line:90%
He lost everything.

00:08:16.140 --> 00:08:19.570 align:middle line:84%
And I looked at that
relative to myself.

00:08:19.570 --> 00:08:21.690 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, what
did I communicate

00:08:21.690 --> 00:08:25.090 align:middle line:84%
that would in any way
have led him to believe

00:08:25.090 --> 00:08:29.730 align:middle line:84%
that all he needed to do
was go inside, visualize,

00:08:29.730 --> 00:08:32.400 align:middle line:84%
imagine, project,
desire, believe,

00:08:32.400 --> 00:08:35.049 align:middle line:84%
and then bring this
reality to himself.

00:08:35.049 --> 00:08:38.679 align:middle line:84%
Now, I had to take stock of
my own part to play in this.

00:08:38.679 --> 00:08:41.700 align:middle line:84%
Because as a teacher-- and
this is the very essence--

00:08:41.700 --> 00:08:44.650 align:middle line:84%
as a teacher, we are totally
responsible for everything

00:08:44.650 --> 00:08:45.290 align:middle line:90%
we teach.

00:08:45.290 --> 00:08:49.070 align:middle line:84%
And if we do not accept
that responsibility,

00:08:49.070 --> 00:08:51.250 align:middle line:84%
my own personal
belief-- doesn't mean

00:08:51.250 --> 00:08:53.770 align:middle line:84%
to say it's true-- my
own personal belief is

00:08:53.770 --> 00:08:58.360 align:middle line:84%
we will pay a price in
our own soul's journey

00:08:58.360 --> 00:09:02.800 align:middle line:84%
for having misled people into
a place where they receive,

00:09:02.800 --> 00:09:08.140 align:middle line:84%
as a result of them placing
their power in our own hands,

00:09:08.140 --> 00:09:10.550 align:middle line:84%
which is what they
tend to do, that there

00:09:10.550 --> 00:09:12.000 align:middle line:90%
is a price that will be paid.

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:15.020 align:middle line:84%
Now, I looked at that,
and I learned a lesson.

00:09:15.020 --> 00:09:18.383 align:middle line:84%
And I think it was a blessing
to learn the lesson very early.

00:09:18.383 --> 00:09:20.930 align:middle line:84%
That the judgment
and guidance that

00:09:20.930 --> 00:09:24.190 align:middle line:84%
is given in any area
of consciousness

00:09:24.190 --> 00:09:28.350 align:middle line:84%
has to be from the authenticity
of your own experience.

00:09:28.350 --> 00:09:31.040 align:middle line:84%
And so this is where we go
back to the Rosicrucians.

00:09:31.040 --> 00:09:32.790 align:middle line:84%
And we go back to
the earlier teachers,

00:09:32.790 --> 00:09:34.570 align:middle line:84%
and we go back to the
Egyptian traditions.

00:09:34.570 --> 00:09:35.860 align:middle line:90%
You go back to the Vedas.

00:09:35.860 --> 00:09:37.260 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't matter.

00:09:37.260 --> 00:09:42.990 align:middle line:84%
We must always be in that
authentic point of truth

00:09:42.990 --> 00:09:46.450 align:middle line:84%
in order to walk through the
door and say to somebody, let

00:09:46.450 --> 00:09:49.270 align:middle line:90%
me tune in closely with you.

00:09:49.270 --> 00:09:52.750 align:middle line:84%
Let me become one with you,
so that when I say something

00:09:52.750 --> 00:09:54.570 align:middle line:90%
to you, it is a truth.

00:09:54.570 --> 00:09:57.460 align:middle line:84%
Not just for me,
but it's because I

00:09:57.460 --> 00:10:02.200 align:middle line:84%
