00:29:28.660 --> 00:29:31.180 align:middle line:84%
The fear of not
knowing who we are.

00:29:31.180 --> 00:29:33.030 align:middle line:90%
Having a meaningful existence.

00:29:33.030 --> 00:29:35.120 align:middle line:90%
Having a purposeful existence.

00:29:35.120 --> 00:29:39.800 align:middle line:84%
Reaching that point
where we realize

00:29:39.800 --> 00:29:42.920 align:middle line:84%
that we've made a
difference on this planet.

00:29:42.920 --> 00:29:46.790 align:middle line:84%
As people move through life, in
the early years, in their 20s

00:29:46.790 --> 00:29:48.590 align:middle line:90%
and maybe 30s, it's like, OK.

00:29:48.590 --> 00:29:50.270 align:middle line:84%
How am I going to
change the world?

00:29:50.270 --> 00:29:52.030 align:middle line:84%
Oh, there's a mind
training program.

00:29:52.030 --> 00:29:53.070 align:middle line:90%
Let me do it.

00:29:53.070 --> 00:29:54.490 align:middle line:90%
And then they'll get results.

00:29:54.490 --> 00:29:56.470 align:middle line:90%
They'll get great results.

00:29:56.470 --> 00:29:59.970 align:middle line:84%
And then, as they get a little
bit older, they start to think,

00:29:59.970 --> 00:30:05.360 align:middle line:84%
you know, but hey, I started
this 30, 40 years ago.

00:30:05.360 --> 00:30:09.120 align:middle line:84%
Mm, have I really
found out who I am?

00:30:09.120 --> 00:30:13.360 align:middle line:84%
I know I can use my mind, and
I know I can bring results.

00:30:13.360 --> 00:30:16.695 align:middle line:84%
But does it always benefit
everybody in my life?

00:30:16.695 --> 00:30:19.752 align:middle line:84%
Have I, in my relationships,
been as positive

00:30:19.752 --> 00:30:20.960 align:middle line:90%
as I would have wanted to be?

00:30:20.960 --> 00:30:23.410 align:middle line:84%
Why did these people
maybe move on?

00:30:23.410 --> 00:30:26.840 align:middle line:84%
And so this self-assessment
is literally

00:30:26.840 --> 00:30:29.010 align:middle line:90%
about self transformation.

00:30:29.010 --> 00:30:32.800 align:middle line:84%
And when people go
to the easy path,

00:30:32.800 --> 00:30:35.540 align:middle line:84%
it is like we go back
to the Rosicrucianism,

00:30:35.540 --> 00:30:36.730 align:middle line:90%
when we started there.

00:30:36.730 --> 00:30:38.460 align:middle line:90%
That was about the work.

00:30:38.460 --> 00:30:40.280 align:middle line:84%
The work of the
mystery schools and all

00:30:40.280 --> 00:30:43.205 align:middle line:84%
the different traditions;
the Theosophists, of BOTA,

00:30:43.205 --> 00:30:43.830 align:middle line:90%
of Golden Door.

00:30:43.830 --> 00:30:45.960 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: These are years-long
training, life-long training.

00:30:45.960 --> 00:30:47.584 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Eventually,
the whole thing--

00:30:47.584 --> 00:30:50.870 align:middle line:84%
it's not a type of-- If you come
in, and you come into my class,

00:30:50.870 --> 00:30:54.100 align:middle line:84%
I will convert your
life overnight.

00:30:54.100 --> 00:30:55.910 align:middle line:84%
Now, this is-- I
know that, because I

00:30:55.910 --> 00:30:57.670 align:middle line:90%
confront that every day.

00:30:57.670 --> 00:31:02.240 align:middle line:84%
Because in the world in which I
live, world in which you live,

00:31:02.240 --> 00:31:04.250 align:middle line:84%
we share the
commonality here, is

00:31:04.250 --> 00:31:07.810 align:middle line:84%
you have to tell people,
these things you will

00:31:07.810 --> 00:31:10.480 align:middle line:90%
get if you come into this room.

00:31:10.480 --> 00:31:13.680 align:middle line:90%
Now, what do I is I get caught.

00:31:13.680 --> 00:31:18.140 align:middle line:84%
It's very, very hard, because
I'm not prepared to say,

00:31:18.140 --> 00:31:23.920 align:middle line:84%
you come in here, and your world
is going to be so different.

00:31:23.920 --> 00:31:26.360 align:middle line:84%
What I am prepared to
say is, if you come in,

00:31:26.360 --> 00:31:28.010 align:middle line:90%
we're going to do some work.

00:31:28.010 --> 00:31:30.300 align:middle line:84%
We're going to
explore some ideas.

00:31:30.300 --> 00:31:33.230 align:middle line:84%
We're going to have
deep, interplaying work,

00:31:33.230 --> 00:31:36.340 align:middle line:84%
and then, when you leave here,
your life will be different.

00:31:36.340 --> 00:31:38.090 align:middle line:84%
But I can't guarantee
when you leave here,

00:31:38.090 --> 00:31:39.600 align:middle line:84%
your life is going
to be fantastic.

00:31:39.600 --> 00:31:40.230 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Or better.

00:31:40.230 --> 00:31:42.790 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: It may actually be a
lot worse because you met me.

00:31:42.790 --> 00:31:43.580 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:31:43.580 --> 00:31:47.730 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: I mean, I met
myself, and I-- but this

00:31:47.730 --> 00:31:48.562 align:middle line:90%
is a possibility.

00:31:48.562 --> 00:31:50.270 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But that's
the part of-- that's

00:31:50.270 --> 00:31:52.430 align:middle line:90%
the point of deep exploration.

00:31:52.430 --> 00:31:56.460 align:middle line:84%
Which again, going back to the
phenomenon in the early 2000s,

00:31:56.460 --> 00:31:59.969 align:middle line:84%
with "The Secret," there
wasn't any depth on--

00:31:59.969 --> 00:32:00.510 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: No.

00:32:00.510 --> 00:32:07.750 align:middle line:84%
And if you actually look,
there is a whole movement now.

00:32:07.750 --> 00:32:09.300 align:middle line:90%
Regina-- my Regina.

00:32:09.300 --> 00:32:10.065 align:middle line:90%
My wife, Regina--

00:32:10.065 --> 00:32:10.470 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yes,
your wife, Regina.

00:32:10.470 --> 00:32:11.090 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: My wife Regina--

00:32:11.090 --> 00:32:11.960 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Two in the same room.

00:32:11.960 --> 00:32:13.918 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: --made a comment
to me the other day,

00:32:13.918 --> 00:32:16.500 align:middle line:84%
and I thought it
was very telling.

00:32:16.500 --> 00:32:20.240 align:middle line:84%
Because we've written
a few books at a time.

00:32:20.240 --> 00:32:24.570 align:middle line:84%
The first one was 650 pages, the
second one was about 650 pages.

00:32:24.570 --> 00:32:26.490 align:middle line:90%
The next one was 460 pages.

00:32:26.490 --> 00:32:28.749 align:middle line:84%
The last one was-- this
one was 170, and the 170--

00:32:28.749 --> 00:32:30.790 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: This one's going
to be five. [CHUCKLES]

00:32:30.790 --> 00:32:31.581 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: Well, no.

00:32:31.581 --> 00:32:33.420 align:middle line:84%
What she said, she was
talking to someone,

00:32:33.420 --> 00:32:35.350 align:middle line:90%
and she reflected back to me.

00:32:35.350 --> 00:32:37.100 align:middle line:84%
She said, have you
noticed how we've

00:32:37.100 --> 00:32:38.740 align:middle line:90%
gone 640 all the way down?

00:32:38.740 --> 00:32:41.840 align:middle line:84%
Then we came down to an
article of three pages.

00:32:41.840 --> 00:32:44.410 align:middle line:90%
Then we came down to a page.

00:32:44.410 --> 00:32:46.227 align:middle line:84%
Then we came down
to a paragraph.

00:32:46.227 --> 00:32:47.560 align:middle line:90%
Then we came down to a sentence.

00:32:47.560 --> 00:32:50.510 align:middle line:84%
Then we came down to
a few power words.

00:32:50.510 --> 00:32:52.370 align:middle line:90%
Then we came down to a key word.

00:32:52.370 --> 00:32:54.950 align:middle line:84%
Then we came down to a
hash tag and an emoticon.

00:32:54.950 --> 00:32:58.850 align:middle line:84%
She said, now, this is
how we are opening up

00:32:58.850 --> 00:33:00.640 align:middle line:90%
levels of consciousness.

00:33:00.640 --> 00:33:03.540 align:middle line:84%
She said, but what
level are we working at?

00:33:03.540 --> 00:33:06.100 align:middle line:84%
She said, what level
are we working at

00:33:06.100 --> 00:33:09.870 align:middle line:84%
to actually be working
with such very, very

00:33:09.870 --> 00:33:11.820 align:middle line:90%
basic-- it's a new language.

00:33:11.820 --> 00:33:12.850 align:middle line:90%
It's a new language.

00:33:12.850 --> 00:33:15.780 align:middle line:84%
It's a new level
of consciousness,

00:33:15.780 --> 00:33:19.000 align:middle line:84%
and it has skipped all
of the foundations.

00:33:19.000 --> 00:33:19.990 align:middle line:90%
It's gone.

00:33:19.990 --> 00:33:20.490 align:middle line:90%
It's gone.

00:33:20.490 --> 00:33:21.150 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: All of the
foundations, yes.

00:33:21.150 --> 00:33:21.650 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:33:21.650 --> 00:33:25.530 align:middle line:84%
So on that, one
of the modalities

00:33:25.530 --> 00:33:28.150 align:middle line:84%
that has been used over
the last 20, 30 years,

00:33:28.150 --> 00:33:31.400 align:middle line:84%
is the notion of-- and I'm going
to use this as an example--

00:33:31.400 --> 00:33:32.940 align:middle line:90%
a vision board.

00:33:32.940 --> 00:33:35.990 align:middle line:84%
So this is really key in
"The Secret" and a lot

00:33:35.990 --> 00:33:38.070 align:middle line:84%
of the different
courses and teachings,

00:33:38.070 --> 00:33:39.614 align:middle line:90%
is you have your vision board.

00:33:39.614 --> 00:33:41.530 align:middle line:84%
And there are different
ways to go about that.

00:33:41.530 --> 00:33:43.095 align:middle line:84%
You choose your
images, your desires.

00:33:43.095 --> 00:33:44.470 align:middle line:84%
You put everything
on your board.

00:33:44.470 --> 00:33:48.760 align:middle line:10%
You look at it, and everything
happens, and you live in bliss.

00:33:48.760 --> 00:33:51.750 align:middle line:84%
Now, that's something
I did, I started

00:33:51.750 --> 00:33:55.230 align:middle line:90%
doing maybe 25 years ago or so.

00:33:55.230 --> 00:33:56.355 align:middle line:90%
I thought, oh, this is fun.

00:33:56.355 --> 00:33:57.770 align:middle line:90%
A vision board.

00:33:57.770 --> 00:34:01.070 align:middle line:84%
And I started watching what
happened through the years,

00:34:01.070 --> 00:34:03.700 align:middle line:84%
because every New Year's,
I would have a vision board

00:34:03.700 --> 00:34:04.200 align:middle line:90%
party.

00:34:04.200 --> 00:34:05.770 align:middle line:84%
So everybody would
bring their magazines,

00:34:05.770 --> 00:34:07.228 align:middle line:84%
have a glass of
champagne, and we'd

00:34:07.228 --> 00:34:09.469 align:middle line:84%
start putting our
vision boards together.

00:34:09.469 --> 00:34:11.020 align:middle line:84%
There were a couple
things about it,

00:34:11.020 --> 00:34:15.580 align:middle line:84%
and I would like you
to key in on the "why"

00:34:15.580 --> 00:34:18.340 align:middle line:90%
for behind what I'm saying.

00:34:18.340 --> 00:34:21.159 align:middle line:84%
One thing I would
have people say is,

00:34:21.159 --> 00:34:23.050 align:middle line:90%
don't think about what you want.

00:34:23.050 --> 00:34:24.889 align:middle line:84%
Don't think about
your desires when

00:34:24.889 --> 00:34:27.239 align:middle line:90%
you go through these images.

00:34:27.239 --> 00:34:31.840 align:middle line:84%
Have a glass of champagne and
go lightly and quickly through.

00:34:31.840 --> 00:34:33.484 align:middle line:84%
And if your gut says
yes, just tear it.

00:34:33.484 --> 00:34:35.010 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't matter what
it is, if it's a word,

00:34:35.010 --> 00:34:35.949 align:middle line:90%
or if it's an image.

00:34:35.949 --> 00:34:38.260 align:middle line:90%
But just only listen to the gut.

00:34:38.260 --> 00:34:38.760 align:middle line:90%
Boom.

00:34:38.760 --> 00:34:39.260 align:middle line:90%
Boom.

00:34:39.260 --> 00:34:40.500 align:middle line:90%
Not the mind.

00:34:40.500 --> 00:34:43.770 align:middle line:84%
And by the end of it, you
end up with a portrait

00:34:43.770 --> 00:34:46.900 align:middle line:90%
of your subconscious desire.

00:34:46.900 --> 00:34:52.630 align:middle line:84%
Now, when done that way, it was
pretty amazing how much of what

00:34:52.630 --> 00:34:56.790 align:middle line:84%
was pinned onto that
board would occur in life.

00:34:56.790 --> 00:34:59.160 align:middle line:84%
When people were using
their minds to override it,

00:34:59.160 --> 00:35:02.450 align:middle line:84%
I need more money, I want to
have a massive, big house,

00:35:02.450 --> 00:35:05.450 align:middle line:84%
and they'd tear those
images out using their mind,

00:35:05.450 --> 00:35:08.360 align:middle line:84%
very little would
manifest on those boards.

00:35:08.360 --> 00:35:12.500 align:middle line:84%
Now, let's talk about-- and
just using that as an example--

00:35:12.500 --> 00:35:16.260 align:middle line:84%
the difference between listening
to a subconscious directive

00:35:16.260 --> 00:35:20.550 align:middle line:84%
versus these desperate desires
or wants or what we think

00:35:20.550 --> 00:35:21.350 align:middle line:90%
are needs.

00:35:21.350 --> 00:35:23.420 align:middle line:84%
And in that, as
you're answering that,

00:35:23.420 --> 00:35:26.250 align:middle line:84%
tell us the story of the woman
who said she wanted $10 million

00:35:26.250 --> 00:35:28.190 align:middle line:90%
in a couple months.

00:35:28.190 --> 00:35:30.370 align:middle line:90%
I love that story.

00:35:30.370 --> 00:35:32.920 align:middle line:84%
Because it gives you a lot to
work with there to explain why

00:35:32.920 --> 00:35:35.730 align:middle line:84%
does one way of doing it
work and the other doesn't.

00:35:35.730 --> 00:35:38.140 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Well
again, in a nutshell,

00:35:38.140 --> 00:35:42.680 align:middle line:84%
it comes back to
authenticity of self.

00:35:42.680 --> 00:35:46.850 align:middle line:84%
It comes back to
understanding desire and what

00:35:46.850 --> 00:35:50.690 align:middle line:84%
desires we hold, at what level
of our being we hold them,

00:35:50.690 --> 00:35:53.360 align:middle line:84%
why we are pursuing
them in the first place.

00:35:53.360 --> 00:35:58.530 align:middle line:84%
Now, I'll give you a couple
of examples to try and put

00:35:58.530 --> 00:35:59.540 align:middle line:90%
this in perspective.

00:35:59.540 --> 00:36:04.560 align:middle line:84%
My mother, and she's
passed, but bless her.

00:36:04.560 --> 00:36:07.999 align:middle line:84%
She actually had
a very good life,

00:36:07.999 --> 00:36:09.290 align:middle line:90%
but she had a challenging life.

00:36:09.290 --> 00:36:11.820 align:middle line:84%
Because from a very,
very early age,

00:36:11.820 --> 00:36:16.740 align:middle line:84%
she was literally
psychic in every way.

00:36:16.740 --> 00:36:19.170 align:middle line:84%
She saw, she knew,
she knew everything.

00:36:19.170 --> 00:36:21.800 align:middle line:84%
This resulted in
her having a series

00:36:21.800 --> 00:36:27.060 align:middle line:84%
of breakdowns and electric shock
treatment and drug treatments.

00:36:27.060 --> 00:36:30.650 align:middle line:84%
I spent the better
part of my childhood

00:36:30.650 --> 00:36:34.570 align:middle line:84%
going to institutions,
where I would see people

00:36:34.570 --> 00:36:38.330 align:middle line:84%
having electric shock treatment
and having drug treatment.

00:36:38.330 --> 00:36:40.310 align:middle line:84%
I saw her many times
when I was a kid.

00:36:40.310 --> 00:36:43.210 align:middle line:84%
I would go every Friday
to these hospitals,

00:36:43.210 --> 00:36:46.730 align:middle line:90%
where the-- what's the word?

00:36:46.730 --> 00:36:47.515 align:middle line:90%
The patients.

00:36:47.515 --> 00:36:48.890 align:middle line:84%
There's got to be
a better world.

00:36:48.890 --> 00:36:51.200 align:middle line:84%
But people who were
in there for reasons

00:36:51.200 --> 00:36:53.180 align:middle line:84%
that weren't of
their own making,

00:36:53.180 --> 00:36:56.630 align:middle line:84%
necessarily, would get together,
and they'd have a dance.

00:36:56.630 --> 00:37:00.530 align:middle line:84%
And I would dance
with these people.

00:37:00.530 --> 00:37:04.420 align:middle line:84%
And there's my mother,
lost, in a void,

00:37:04.420 --> 00:37:07.500 align:middle line:84%
because she had
been reprogrammed

00:37:07.500 --> 00:37:10.840 align:middle line:84%
by the use of drugs and
electroshock treatment.

00:37:10.840 --> 00:37:13.200 align:middle line:84%
Now, the reason
I mention that is

00:37:13.200 --> 00:37:16.010 align:middle line:84%
because she had a
very powerful mind,

00:37:16.010 --> 00:37:17.552 align:middle line:90%
and she had a wonderful heart.

00:37:17.552 --> 00:37:20.830 align:middle line:84%
And what happened was,
she came from a base

00:37:20.830 --> 00:37:23.610 align:middle line:84%
of fear, which is
why I mentioned fear

00:37:23.610 --> 00:37:25.520 align:middle line:90%
in the beginning.

00:37:25.520 --> 00:37:28.750 align:middle line:84%
She always had a fear
that she simply wouldn't

00:37:28.750 --> 00:37:29.750 align:middle line:90%
have what was necessary.

00:37:29.750 --> 00:37:33.060 align:middle line:84%
And that went back to the
wartime, the childhood wartime

00:37:33.060 --> 00:37:35.970 align:middle line:84%
and the loss of someone
she loved in the war.

00:37:35.970 --> 00:37:39.040 align:middle line:84%
Now, when I step
forward in time,

00:37:39.040 --> 00:37:42.690 align:middle line:84%
she ended up coming to one of
my programs in the early years.

00:37:42.690 --> 00:37:44.910 align:middle line:84%
So she's sitting
there, all proud,

00:37:44.910 --> 00:37:47.320 align:middle line:90%
the way mothers do what they do.

00:37:47.320 --> 00:37:50.940 align:middle line:84%
And she suddenly
gets it in her mind

00:37:50.940 --> 00:37:54.250 align:middle line:84%
that if I use what
he's saying, I might

00:37:54.250 --> 00:37:56.660 align:middle line:90%
be able to get some results.

00:37:56.660 --> 00:38:00.590 align:middle line:84%
So she decides she's going
to work with her mind

00:38:00.590 --> 00:38:01.770 align:middle line:90%
to bring about some results.

00:38:01.770 --> 00:38:04.700 align:middle line:84%
Well, she'd already proven that
she had a very powerful mind,

00:38:04.700 --> 00:38:07.240 align:middle line:84%
because she took herself
down the path of great pain

00:38:07.240 --> 00:38:08.602 align:middle line:90%
and suffering.

00:38:08.602 --> 00:38:10.060 align:middle line:84%
So one day, she
decides she's going

00:38:10.060 --> 00:38:11.970 align:middle line:90%
to go in for a competition.

00:38:11.970 --> 00:38:14.040 align:middle line:84%
So she goes in for
this competition,

00:38:14.040 --> 00:38:18.200 align:middle line:84%
and it's for a trip around
Australia on a cruise ship,

00:38:18.200 --> 00:38:19.603 align:middle line:90%
and it's all expenses paid.

00:38:19.603 --> 00:38:20.410 align:middle line:90%
Done up.

00:38:20.410 --> 00:38:22.910 align:middle line:84%
She's in the shopping center,
this is going back to the time

00:38:22.910 --> 00:38:25.160 align:middle line:84%
when you didn't have
the internet and that.

00:38:25.160 --> 00:38:27.480 align:middle line:90%
And she's right at the back.

00:38:27.480 --> 00:38:29.530 align:middle line:84%
And she's-- you've got
to be present to win.

00:38:29.530 --> 00:38:31.920 align:middle line:84%
So she's standing back, and
the guy's announcing it.

00:38:31.920 --> 00:38:33.310 align:middle line:90%
She couldn't hear anything.

00:38:33.310 --> 00:38:36.870 align:middle line:84%
So she's thinking, well, all
these people are missing out.

00:38:36.870 --> 00:38:38.370 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I can't
hear, so they can't.

00:38:38.370 --> 00:38:42.010 align:middle line:84%
So she goes forward after
the second name's been drawn.

00:38:42.010 --> 00:38:43.010 align:middle line:90%
And she says, excuse me.

00:38:43.010 --> 00:38:45.270 align:middle line:84%
She said, dear, nobody
can hear what's going on.

00:38:45.270 --> 00:38:46.180 align:middle line:90%
He said, I apologize.

00:38:46.180 --> 00:38:49.495 align:middle line:84%
So as she turns around, he
goes, Mrs. Taylor of Willagee.

00:38:49.495 --> 00:38:51.599 align:middle line:90%
And she goes, oh, that's me.

00:38:51.599 --> 00:38:52.390 align:middle line:90%
So she goes around.

00:38:52.390 --> 00:38:55.330 align:middle line:84%
She opens-- so she wins,
and she gets this trip.

00:38:55.330 --> 00:38:57.020 align:middle line:90%
Now, wait for this.

00:38:57.020 --> 00:39:00.140 align:middle line:84%
She then proceeds to win,
because she won that one thing,

00:39:00.140 --> 00:39:01.820 align:middle line:90%
she won the lottery.

00:39:01.820 --> 00:39:03.770 align:middle line:84%
Her name was called
out as the viewer

00:39:03.770 --> 00:39:08.600 align:middle line:84%
on "The Wheel of Fortune,"
and she won $30,000 on that.

00:39:08.600 --> 00:39:09.630 align:middle line:90%
She won a caravan.

00:39:09.630 --> 00:39:10.960 align:middle line:90%
She won a trip to America.

00:39:10.960 --> 00:39:13.190 align:middle line:84%
She won-- and it went
from one to the other.

00:39:13.190 --> 00:39:18.550 align:middle line:84%
Now, all of a sudden,
everything stopped.

00:39:18.550 --> 00:39:20.620 align:middle line:90%
And she went into a hole.

00:39:20.620 --> 00:39:25.420 align:middle line:84%
And what happened for
everything to come to a halt

00:39:25.420 --> 00:39:27.470 align:middle line:90%
was my father got ill.

00:39:27.470 --> 00:39:31.310 align:middle line:84%
And when she thought she
was going to lose him,

00:39:31.310 --> 00:39:35.860 align:middle line:84%
every fear she had ever
had rose to the surface,

00:39:35.860 --> 00:39:39.310 align:middle line:84%
and then everything she
had just left her, apart

00:39:39.310 --> 00:39:44.250 align:middle line:84%
from her fear and her husband,
who was ailing at the time.

00:39:44.250 --> 00:39:46.586 align:middle line:90%
So she went through.

00:39:46.586 --> 00:39:47.960 align:middle line:84%
She did all the
different things.

00:39:47.960 --> 00:39:49.560 align:middle line:90%
She proved it could work.

00:39:49.560 --> 00:39:52.860 align:middle line:84%
But then, at the time
of the greatest need,

00:39:52.860 --> 00:39:55.520 align:middle line:84%
the point where she was,
was the deepest issue,

00:39:55.520 --> 00:39:59.120 align:middle line:84%
which was the fear of the
loss of love, rose up.

00:39:59.120 --> 00:40:01.010 align:middle line:90%
It canceled everything else out.

00:40:01.010 --> 00:40:03.010 align:middle line:84%
All the joy, all the
fear, of all the desires

00:40:03.010 --> 00:40:07.180 align:middle line:84%
and all the attachments,
which she deserved.

00:40:07.180 --> 00:40:11.610 align:middle line:84%
They meant nothing, because
the one thing she really wanted

00:40:11.610 --> 00:40:13.697 align:middle line:84%
was love, and she did
not want to lose it.

00:40:13.697 --> 00:40:14.280 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:40:14.280 --> 00:40:15.946 align:middle line:84%
And that was the point
I was getting to,

00:40:15.946 --> 00:40:17.600 align:middle line:90%
that authentic part of it.

00:40:17.600 --> 00:40:20.470 align:middle line:84%
Back with people putting
their images on their board.

00:40:20.470 --> 00:40:21.930 align:middle line:90%
There's I need this.

00:40:21.930 --> 00:40:22.650 align:middle line:90%
I need that.

00:40:22.650 --> 00:40:23.895 align:middle line:90%
Oh gosh, I need a new sink.

00:40:23.895 --> 00:40:24.395 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:40:24.395 --> 00:40:25.870 align:middle line:90%
I'll put a sink on there.

00:40:25.870 --> 00:40:26.680 align:middle line:90%
No, need, need.

00:40:26.680 --> 00:40:28.750 align:middle line:90%
All that was fear driven.

00:40:28.750 --> 00:40:32.430 align:middle line:84%
These never-- and "The Secret"
didn't-- and just using "The

00:40:32.430 --> 00:40:36.245 align:middle line:84%
Secret" again, it didn't
differentiate these mindsets.

00:40:36.245 --> 00:40:36.870 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: Yeah.

00:40:36.870 --> 00:40:38.991 align:middle line:90%
Because it's the old story.

00:40:38.991 --> 00:40:41.490 align:middle line:84%
Be careful what you ask for,
because you're going to get it.

00:40:41.490 --> 00:40:44.234 align:middle line:84%
And what you tend
to get-- see, when

00:40:44.234 --> 00:40:46.900 align:middle line:84%
we were in our conversation, and
this is in context of where you

00:40:46.900 --> 00:40:55.610 align:middle line:84%
are here, is that the principle
of working with consciousness

00:40:55.610 --> 00:41:01.590 align:middle line:84%
is that we have moved from
a model of mechanistic,

00:41:01.590 --> 00:41:05.450 align:middle line:84%
in other words, the
random god force, which

00:41:05.450 --> 00:41:12.280 align:middle line:84%
has got no type of life in
it, into one of understanding

00:41:12.280 --> 00:41:16.470 align:middle line:84%
the implicate order
which underlies

00:41:16.470 --> 00:41:20.200 align:middle line:84%
all of the laws of
the entire cosmos.

00:41:20.200 --> 00:41:22.905 align:middle line:84%
Now, what I would
say to you is this--

00:41:22.905 --> 00:41:24.530 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Without
going all Bohm on us,

00:41:24.530 --> 00:41:25.654 align:middle line:90%
just give us what you mean.

00:41:25.654 --> 00:41:30.560 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: What I
suggest to you is this.

00:41:30.560 --> 00:41:39.480 align:middle line:84%
Is that the whole of creation is
based upon a fabric of law that

00:41:39.480 --> 00:41:44.620 align:middle line:84%
works fundamentally,
according to very, very, very

00:41:44.620 --> 00:41:49.580 align:middle line:84%
deterministic,
deterministic principles.

00:41:49.580 --> 00:41:53.700 align:middle line:90%
We will not know the outcome.

00:41:53.700 --> 00:41:57.430 align:middle line:84%
But the outcome is
already determined,

00:41:57.430 --> 00:42:02.210 align:middle line:84%
because the
conditions of the law

00:42:02.210 --> 00:42:08.670 align:middle line:84%
are such that they will always
respond in infinite ways

00:42:08.670 --> 00:42:12.380 align:middle line:84%
according to the principle
of harmony and balance.

00:42:12.380 --> 00:42:15.910 align:middle line:84%
Harmony and balance is
the fundamental principle

00:42:15.910 --> 00:42:19.030 align:middle line:84%
on which the implicate
order-- it's not chaos.

00:42:19.030 --> 00:42:21.770 align:middle line:90%
It's not any of this.

00:42:21.770 --> 00:42:24.180 align:middle line:84%
It's always going to
take us back to harmony.

00:42:24.180 --> 00:42:26.247 align:middle line:84%
So when we look at
vision boarding,

00:42:26.247 --> 00:42:28.330 align:middle line:84%
and we would look at putting
things on the board--

00:42:28.330 --> 00:42:29.390 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Talk
about the lady who

00:42:29.390 --> 00:42:31.330 align:middle line:84%
you were talking with that
said, I want $10 million.

00:42:31.330 --> 00:42:31.871 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: OK.

00:42:31.871 --> 00:42:35.100 align:middle line:84%
So some time ago, this
lady was sitting next to me

00:42:35.100 --> 00:42:36.320 align:middle line:90%
in a program.

00:42:36.320 --> 00:42:39.740 align:middle line:84%
I was there participating
as a speaker.

00:42:39.740 --> 00:42:43.260 align:middle line:84%
And the speaker at the
time said, would you

00:42:43.260 --> 00:42:46.810 align:middle line:84%
share with people whatever your
goals, et cetera, would be.

00:42:46.810 --> 00:42:50.360 align:middle line:84%
Now, I don't know even
if I shared a goal.

00:42:50.360 --> 00:42:52.170 align:middle line:84%
And there's a reason
for that, and I'll

00:42:52.170 --> 00:42:53.810 align:middle line:90%
explain that afterwards.

00:42:53.810 --> 00:42:57.290 align:middle line:84%
But she turned to
me, and she said,

00:42:57.290 --> 00:43:05.140 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to manifest $10
million by the end of the year.

00:43:05.140 --> 00:43:07.570 align:middle line:84%
That gave her around about
four months or five months.

00:43:07.570 --> 00:43:09.320 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And she was
broke at the moment?

00:43:09.320 --> 00:43:12.630 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: You're coming from a
base of being basically broke.

00:43:12.630 --> 00:43:15.169 align:middle line:84%
Now, my feedback
after the event, this

00:43:15.169 --> 00:43:16.460 align:middle line:90%
wasn't a program I was running.

00:43:16.460 --> 00:43:20.030 align:middle line:84%
But my feedback after the event
was that she went further down

00:43:20.030 --> 00:43:21.820 align:middle line:90%
the hole afterwards.

00:43:21.820 --> 00:43:24.600 align:middle line:84%
Because you see,
you can't actually

00:43:24.600 --> 00:43:29.730 align:middle line:84%
tell some folk, honey,
bear with me on this.

00:43:29.730 --> 00:43:35.060 align:middle line:84%
How deeply do you understand
the principles of consciousness

00:43:35.060 --> 00:43:36.910 align:middle line:84%
that you're going
to bring this in?

00:43:36.910 --> 00:43:41.290 align:middle line:84%
Now, she believed that there
was a system and a process.

00:43:41.290 --> 00:43:43.830 align:middle line:84%
But it wasn't even
a matter of belief.

00:43:43.830 --> 00:43:47.000 align:middle line:84%
It was that she had
grasped hold of something

00:43:47.000 --> 00:43:48.760 align:middle line:90%
without the foundation.

00:43:48.760 --> 00:43:51.400 align:middle line:84%
And if I do this and
this, it's got to happen,

00:43:51.400 --> 00:43:53.910 align:middle line:84%
because the law
says it will happen.

00:43:53.910 --> 00:43:55.250 align:middle line:90%
And it didn't happen.

00:43:55.250 --> 00:43:57.265 align:middle line:84%
And that was another
life which went off

00:43:57.265 --> 00:44:00.890 align:middle line:84%
down the track into--
well, I can't say oblivion.

00:44:00.890 --> 00:44:03.237 align:middle line:84%
But see, that's where
the lessons come in.

00:44:03.237 --> 00:44:04.570 align:middle line:90%
And this is one of the beauties.

00:44:04.570 --> 00:44:06.830 align:middle line:84%
When you started
our conversation,

00:44:06.830 --> 00:44:10.860 align:middle line:84%
your point was, if I
recall rightly, you said,

00:44:10.860 --> 00:44:12.949 align:middle line:84%
all these people that
are involved in New Age,

00:44:12.949 --> 00:44:13.740 align:middle line:90%
I'm involved in it.

00:44:13.740 --> 00:44:14.960 align:middle line:90%
You're involved in it.

00:44:14.960 --> 00:44:17.630 align:middle line:84%
How come so many people's
lives are a mess?

00:44:17.630 --> 00:44:18.941 align:middle line:90%
How come--

00:44:18.941 --> 00:44:20.190 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Not very functional.

00:44:20.190 --> 00:44:21.750 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Yeah, not
very functional.

00:44:21.750 --> 00:44:24.820 align:middle line:84%
And one of the reasons
is quite simply

00:44:24.820 --> 00:44:28.040 align:middle line:84%
that we don't look at--
even by doing things.

00:44:28.040 --> 00:44:31.150 align:middle line:84%
Let's say we took everything
that's given in "The Secret"

00:44:31.150 --> 00:44:33.900 align:middle line:84%
and in vision boarding
and at face value,

00:44:33.900 --> 00:44:35.860 align:middle line:84%
and saying, this is
really good stuff.

00:44:35.860 --> 00:44:39.695 align:middle line:84%
Which it has got great
merit in the right context.

00:44:39.695 --> 00:44:41.280 align:middle line:90%
In the right context.

00:44:41.280 --> 00:44:44.790 align:middle line:84%
But let's say that we work
with those principles.

00:44:44.790 --> 00:44:47.120 align:middle line:84%
If the principles
do not give us what

00:44:47.120 --> 00:44:49.950 align:middle line:84%
we want, and we end up
with say, a divorce,

00:44:49.950 --> 00:44:52.949 align:middle line:84%
or we end up in a car accident,
because we're so upset--

00:44:52.949 --> 00:44:54.240 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That we lose our job?

00:44:54.240 --> 00:44:57.020 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: We've lost our job,
or we got sick or something.

00:44:57.020 --> 00:45:00.670 align:middle line:84%
That's the door which all of
the great mystery traditions

00:45:00.670 --> 00:45:02.330 align:middle line:90%
said walk through.

00:45:02.330 --> 00:45:05.850 align:middle line:84%
Because if you walk through that
door, that is your initiation.

00:45:05.850 --> 00:45:06.740 align:middle line:90%
That is your death.

00:45:06.740 --> 00:45:08.300 align:middle line:84%
And when you have
that death, that

00:45:08.300 --> 00:45:11.462 align:middle line:84%
is when the light will come, and
then you will look at who are,

00:45:11.462 --> 00:45:13.670 align:middle line:84%
and you will realize you
didn't want any of the stuff

00:45:13.670 --> 00:45:15.910 align:middle line:84%
you put on the board
in the first instance.

00:45:15.910 --> 00:45:17.980 align:middle line:84%
What you wanted, to
walk through that door.

00:45:17.980 --> 00:45:19.480 align:middle line:84%
And when you walk
through that door,

00:45:19.480 --> 00:45:21.340 align:middle line:90%
that is exactly what you wanted.

00:45:21.340 --> 00:45:23.656 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So the naivete that
made a person-- took them

00:45:23.656 --> 00:45:26.280 align:middle line:84%
down that road to show up at the
conference in the first place,

00:45:26.280 --> 00:45:28.071 align:middle line:84%
with the idea, I
need $10 million--

00:45:28.071 --> 00:45:30.320 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to make $10 million
in the next four months.

00:45:30.320 --> 00:45:31.630 align:middle line:90%
It's going to come to me.

00:45:31.630 --> 00:45:33.990 align:middle line:90%
That's extreme naivete.

00:45:33.990 --> 00:45:37.960 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Or, or there is
a distinct possibility,

00:45:37.960 --> 00:45:42.070 align:middle line:84%
and I put this in context
of our first discussion,

00:45:42.070 --> 00:45:45.920 align:middle line:84%
that a lot of it is the mass
cultural hypnosis of our times.

00:45:45.920 --> 00:45:49.030 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: We're going to go
into that in just a minute.

00:45:49.030 --> 00:45:51.460 align:middle line:84%
But let's say the average
person is naive enough

00:45:51.460 --> 00:45:52.962 align:middle line:90%
to believe that, OK.

00:45:52.962 --> 00:45:54.420 align:middle line:84%
If I just think
about it every day,

00:45:54.420 --> 00:45:57.920 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to have $10 million
in four months, not knowing

00:45:57.920 --> 00:46:01.440 align:middle line:84%
that the acquisition of money
is yet another skill set that

00:46:01.440 --> 00:46:04.080 align:middle line:84%
has been groomed by people
that have a lot of money,

00:46:04.080 --> 00:46:08.200 align:middle line:84%
over perhaps lifetimes, to learn
to amass that kind of money.

00:46:08.200 --> 00:46:11.675 align:middle line:84%
Without any of even those
kinds of basic underpinnings

00:46:11.675 --> 00:46:14.450 align:middle line:84%
on a karmic level,
it's native to think

00:46:14.450 --> 00:46:15.710 align:middle line:90%
that's going to happen.

00:46:15.710 --> 00:46:17.710 align:middle line:84%
So I'm going to just--
for the most part--

00:46:17.710 --> 00:46:20.060 align:middle line:84%
put it in the
category of naivete.

00:46:20.060 --> 00:46:23.110 align:middle line:84%
But that very naivete, as
you're saying, is the gift.

00:46:23.110 --> 00:46:23.740 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: Yes.

00:46:23.740 --> 00:46:26.250 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Because that naivete
leads to the broken heart,

00:46:26.250 --> 00:46:29.180 align:middle line:84%
the disappointment takes
us through the door

00:46:29.180 --> 00:46:32.910 align:middle line:84%
to our actual growth in the
beginning of establishing what

00:46:32.910 --> 00:46:35.010 align:middle line:90%
is our authentic self and path.

00:46:35.010 --> 00:46:35.700 align:middle line:90%
Know thyself.

00:46:35.700 --> 00:46:36.330 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: Yes.

00:46:36.330 --> 00:46:36.780 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:46:36.780 --> 00:46:37.170 align:middle line:90%
Exactly.

00:46:37.170 --> 00:46:38.379 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So it's not wasted.

00:46:38.379 --> 00:46:38.919 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: No.

00:46:38.919 --> 00:46:39.500 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:46:39.500 --> 00:46:41.625 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Unless you just
go off, and disappointed,

00:46:41.625 --> 00:46:43.010 align:middle line:90%
and do something-- nothing.

00:46:43.010 --> 00:46:43.210 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: No.

00:46:43.210 --> 00:46:43.710 align:middle line:90%
Look, look.

00:46:43.710 --> 00:46:46.720 align:middle line:84%
I mean, if-- I'm sure
we're both the same.

00:46:46.720 --> 00:46:50.220 align:middle line:84%
We've probably explored
so many different things.

00:46:50.220 --> 00:46:52.900 align:middle line:84%
I have had teachers and teachers
and teachers and teachers,

00:46:52.900 --> 00:46:55.770 align:middle line:84%
and I would not be
in my own position

00:46:55.770 --> 00:46:59.290 align:middle line:84%
if I hadn't have had teachers
who I greatly revered

00:46:59.290 --> 00:47:02.440 align:middle line:84%
and teachers who I
wanted to shy away from,

00:47:02.440 --> 00:47:04.600 align:middle line:84%
because they were some
of the best teachers.

00:47:04.600 --> 00:47:09.110 align:middle line:84%
Some of the ones that in an--
and by the way, in saying this,

00:47:09.110 --> 00:47:12.330 align:middle line:84%
I'm not suggesting for one
second I know the answers.

00:47:12.330 --> 00:47:14.300 align:middle line:84%
What I'm saying is
these are observations

00:47:14.300 --> 00:47:15.280 align:middle line:90%
that have been made.

00:47:15.280 --> 00:47:18.530 align:middle line:84%
But some of the teachers who
have told me to do things

00:47:18.530 --> 00:47:24.290 align:middle line:84%
have pushed other buttons which
have forced me maybe to get

00:47:24.290 --> 00:47:26.350 align:middle line:84%
upset with myself,
because I'm upset

00:47:26.350 --> 00:47:27.710 align:middle line:90%
with what they told me to do.

00:47:27.710 --> 00:47:30.030 align:middle line:84%
And that forces me
to go somewhere else

00:47:30.030 --> 00:47:31.370 align:middle line:90%
to find my answers.

00:47:31.370 --> 00:47:33.770 align:middle line:84%
So they all, every
single one of them,

00:47:33.770 --> 00:47:36.757 align:middle line:84%
serves a purpose,
and a very good one.

00:47:36.757 --> 00:47:37.340 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:47:37.340 --> 00:47:38.931 align:middle line:84%
But now, let's go
on another track

00:47:38.931 --> 00:47:40.930 align:middle line:84%
which you just alluded
to a moment ago, the mass

00:47:40.930 --> 00:47:42.690 align:middle line:90%
cultural hypnosis.

00:47:42.690 --> 00:47:46.365 align:middle line:84%
Do you think there have been
movements and teachers placed,

00:47:46.365 --> 00:47:49.390 align:middle line:84%
or who have placed themselves,
or in tandem with perhaps

00:47:49.390 --> 00:47:52.330 align:middle line:84%
shadowy organizations
and whatnot,

00:47:52.330 --> 00:47:56.420 align:middle line:84%
in place to literally
distract people

00:47:56.420 --> 00:48:00.610 align:middle line:84%
from their own
potential power in life

00:48:00.610 --> 00:48:03.740 align:middle line:90%
through the New Age movement?

00:48:03.740 --> 00:48:08.490 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: I believe-- and again,
this is a perception of my own.

00:48:08.490 --> 00:48:10.720 align:middle line:90%
I believe that is so.

00:48:10.720 --> 00:48:17.350 align:middle line:84%
That there are-- if we took
it in context of the Bible

00:48:17.350 --> 00:48:20.990 align:middle line:84%
teachings, and I'm not
a biblical scholar.

00:48:20.990 --> 00:48:23.612 align:middle line:84%
But if we took it in context
of the Bible's teachings,

00:48:23.612 --> 00:48:25.820 align:middle line:84%
it's like there would be
prophets and false prophets,

00:48:25.820 --> 00:48:27.230 align:middle line:90%
et cetera, et cetera.

00:48:27.230 --> 00:48:31.420 align:middle line:84%
Now, I mean, for a lot of
folks who follow very, very

00:48:31.420 --> 00:48:34.670 align:middle line:84%
